Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Ottawa economic summit
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wgjg
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 26 Jul 1981
Middle East unrest dominates news from Ottawa summit. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.